Print a Summary for a compilr object

Source: R/summary.R
print.compilr.Rd

Print a Summary for a compilr object

Usage

# S3 method for compilr
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

An object of class compilr.

...

Other arguments passed to summary.compilr.

See also

summary.compilr

Examples


cilr <- compilr(data = mcompd, sbp = sbp, 
                parts = c("TST", "WAKE", "MVPA", "LPA", "SB"), 
                idvar = "ID")
print(cilr)
